This is the digital painting from the official Porsche designer, Ben Baum. Ben Baum participated in the design of the whole process of Turbo S model. He kept the DNA of Porsche classic design with a different thinking from other designers and constantly explored the design language.

Ben Baum grew up in Black Forest, Germany, and studied industrial design in Graz, Austria. He also studied the automotive industry at Strate College Paris. During the nine years at Porsche, Ben Baum participated in the design of many famous designs.

Leo Liang，NFT digital artist , who is good at interpreting a dialogue between the inner world and self with elegant and fashionable works. The conception of the subject matter and the context of creation are derived from the feelings and reflections of the constant accumulation and transformation of aesthetics during the years of jewelry creation and collage art. The works are dark, elegant and fashionable, with multiple expressions, and sometimes they can completely escape and present a new atmosphere. In the creation, based on the belief that "art that touches others can give people a supreme strength ", In 2021, three collage works were selected for the " Mellow Art Award 2020 "Japan Art Awards, and nine NFT works Shortlister in the first "NFT World Masters "at Art Revolution Taipei, and won the second prize in the "BCA Global Young Digital Art Scholarship Program" competition. And TheOne.art "The world's first digital art creation competition" was shortlisted.

Duansen graduated from Xi 'an Academy of Fine Arts and works as an artistic director of Digital Art Development Center of Urban Sculpture Committee of China Culture Promotion Association. He has worked as the director of the digital modeling department in Zhang Huan Studio. Some of his works have been exhibited in Shaanxi Art Museum and shortlisted for MJH&Design Week Art Plan International Competition. He has participated in the red digital sculpture online exhibition commemorating the 100th anniversary of the founding of the Communist Party of China.
